<p class="">Is the right hon. Gentleman aware that there is a huge and growing area in Scotland devoted to deer forests and that not only is that land itself barren, but the existence and increasing numbers of the deer, cause other land, bordering upon it, to be devastated from an agricultural point of view?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
